<div id="review_3923288102" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3923288102" />
    <a title="Linda" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3928093-linda"><img alt="Linda" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1343494664p2/3928093.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3923288102?book_show_action=true">Apr 02, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Linda" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Linda" href="/user/show/3928093-linda">Linda</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/21006376-paul-and-virginia-from-the-french-of-j-b-h-de-saint-pierre">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3928093-linda?shelf=classics">classics</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3923288102" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10330477107370113606">Two French women on Mauritius raise their two children in an unstructured idyllic lifestyle. The children fall in love, having spent their lives as brother and sister, and when the girl goes to France, the boy suffers dramatically. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

