<li class='cover' id='bookCover_3077927'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3077927"><img alt="ماجدولين" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1206190962l/3077927._SX98_.jpg" />
