<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer16265321026102177075">Jacques-Henri Bernardin de Saint-Pierre was a French writer and botanist. He is best known for his 1788 novel <i>Paul et Virginie</i>, now largely forgotten, but in the 19th century a very popular children&apos;s book.</span>
  <span id="freeText16265321026102177075" style="display:none">Jacques-Henri Bernardin de Saint-Pierre was a French writer and botanist. He is best known for his 1788 novel <i>Paul et Virginie</i>, now largely forgotten, but in the 19th century a very popular children's book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16265321026102177075" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

